<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-DfXdz2htPH0lsSSs5nCTpuj/zy4C+OGpamoFVy38MVBnE+IbbVYUew+OrCXaRkfj" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.0/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-Q6E9RHvbIyZFJoft+2mJbHaEWldlvI9IOYy5n3zV9zzTtmI3UksdQRVvoxMfooAo" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.0/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-OgVRvuATP1z7JjHLkuOU7Xw704+h835Lr+6QL9UvYjZE3Ipu6Tp75j7Bh/kR0JKI" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.0/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-9aIt2nRpC12Uk9gS9baDl411NQApFmC26EwAOH8WgZl5MYYxFfc+NcPb1dKGj7Sk" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/selection.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/nav.css">
    <title>Panel || JobFest </title>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light bg-light">
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">JobFest</a>
        <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbarSupportedContent" aria-controls="navbarSupportedContent" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
          <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
        </button>
      
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarSupportedContent">
          <ul class="navbar-nav ml-auto" style="margin-right: 200px;">
            <li class="nav-item active">
              <a class="nav-link" href="/api/user/selection">Home<span class="sr-only">(current)</span></a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="nav-link" href="/api/user/feeds">Feeds</a>
            </li>
            <% if(type=="Admin"){ %>
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="nav-link" href="/api/user/candidates">Candidates</a>
            </li>
            <% } else { %>
              <li class="nav-item">
                <a class="nav-link" href="/api/user/profile">Profile</a>
              </li>
            <% } %>
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="nav-link" href="http://127.0.0.1:5000/">Predictor </a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item dropdown">
              <a class="nav-link dropdown-toggle" href="#" id="navbarDropdown" role="button" data-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false">
                Settings
              </a>
              <div class="dropdown-menu" aria-labelledby="navbarDropdown">
                <center>
                  <form action="/api/user/logout" method="POST">
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-warning">Logout</button>           
                  </form><br>
                  <form action="/api/user/deleteaccount/<%= user.id %>" method="POST">
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-danger">Delete</button>           
                  </form>
                </center>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </nav>
      <div style="display: flex;" class="panel">
        <% if(type=="Admin"){ %>
          <div class="talkingtoemployer">
            <h1>Hello!</h1>
            <p>
              Do you know that India is going to face a serious financial crisis after this pandemic is done? In the post 
              pandemic situation, it it expected that few lakhs of people will lose their job. Not only the wage earners but 
              the engineers, IT professionals and even technicians will also lose their job. If you can provide a job, to 
              reduce unemployment, please do the same! Thanks!
            </p>
            <div style="display: flex;">
              <form action="/api/user/employer" method="GET">
                <input type="submit" value="Post a Job" class="btn btn-primary">
            </form>
            <form action="/api/user/postedjobs" method="GET">
              <input type="submit" value="Posted Jobs" class="btn btn-info" style="margin-left: 10px;;">
            </form>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% }else{ %>
          <div class="talkingtoemployer">
            <h1>Hello!</h1>
            <p>
              Are you searching for a job my friend? No worries, JobFest has thousands of jobs which can save you from unemployment.
              You can pickup any job as per your liking and skills. You can enjoy the time working and earning few extra bucks to
              happily sustain the post pandemic situation.
            </p>
            <form action="/api/user/dashboard" method="GET">
              <input type="submit" value="Find a Job" class="btn btn-warning">
            </form>
          </div>
        <% } %> 
      </div>
      <footer>
        <style>.heart{color:#e25555;}</style>
        <p style="color: white; font-size: 20px;">Made with <span class="heart">‚ù§</span> in India</p>
      </footer>
</body>
</html>